Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 4.14 10/28] ASoC: Intel: atom: Take the drv->lock mutex before calling sst_send_slot_map()
Date:   Sat, 18 Apr 2020 10:43:10 -0400
Message-Id: <20200418144328.10265-10-sashal@kernel.org>
